  .container
    header
      h2 About Us
      span.line

    .row
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-md-5.col-lg-6.text
        h3 We love to turn ideas into beautiful apps
        p We are local Denver experts in complex database driven websites that leverage Ruby on Rails for rapid development of fully tested, scalable web applications. We are developing topnotch applications for iPhone/iPad and Android devices. Our team is passionate about building new tools and services for our clients. There is nothing more exciting than to watch a startup succeed. We want to be part of it, and we can help by developing great software.

