        h3 Mobile Development
        p The development of a mobile app for your business should be an integral piece of your overall marketing strategy. After all, the popularity of these apps is continuously increasing, and iPhone users alone have downloaded more than 27 billion applications from a wide variety of companies.

    .row.to-right
      .pic.col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-md-5.col-lg-6
        img.img-responsive src="images/feature2.png"

      .info.col-xs-12.col-sm-7.col-md-7.col-lg-6
        h3 Web Development
        p Open source and one of the fastest web development frameworks around, Ruby on Rails is our technology of choice. We use it for the majority of our software projects.

    .row
      .pic.col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-md-5.col-lg-6
