      .info.col-xs-12.col-sm-7.col-md-7.col-lg-6
        h3 UX/UI Design
        p The final look and feel of a digital application—the user interface (UI). These designs are aimed to exceed user expectations by marrying a product’s interface architecture with an aesthetic and user experience (UX) that brings it to life.

